---
title: Seared Salmon & Rosemary Sauce with Creamy Parsnip Mash & Mayo
description: You know you’re in for a good night when the only thing standing between you and a quality meal is a matter of minutes! With a cut of
beef eye round, buttery rosemary sauce and a parsnip mash, you can’t go wrong.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-and-mash-with-rosemary-sauce-b5d441d5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/salmon-and-mash-with-rosemary-sauce-60fe25586df8dd6ebd40d986-648aee52.pdf
